        Product Benefits Over-the-counter upset stomach reliever

        About this item

        • Rapid Nausea Relief - Get fast relief from your stomach aches and nausea with Emetrol Liquid - Non-Drowsy. The cherry flavored liquid provides quick relief from tummy upset. Treat your family's nausea that is caused by food poisoning, overindulgence in food and drink, motion sickness, or car sickness.
        • Calm Your Stomach - Emetrol calms your stomach by treating the source of nausea and relaxing the stomach muscles. Other medications only coat the stomach and are so sometimes not as effective or quick. Emetrol helps stomach muscles relax so that your family can find relief from stomach pain and nausea.
        • A Trusted Brand - Feel confident that you're getting the best nausea relief medication out there for your family. For over 60 years Emetrol has been the #1 Pharmacist recommended over-the-counter medication for nausea and stomach pain relief for adults and children. That's because it really works.
        • Powerful Relief - Emetrol's liquid active ingredients calms your stomach quickly. Phosphoric Acid, Dextrose, and Levulose work quickly to relieve your upset stomach. Emetrol provides powerful relief without using aspirin, antihistamines, alcohol or caffeine, making it a safe and effective medication for your family's stomach pain.
        • Easy to Take - Adults and children older than 12 can take 15 to 30 milliliters at onset of nausea symptoms. Children ages 2 to 12 can take 5 to 10 milliliters. The dosage can be repeated every 15 minutes until symptoms subside. Unless advised by a doctor, do not exceed 5 doses within an hour.

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
